Dear Mrs. Safieh,

Thank you for registering to attend your upcoming UOWD Graduation Ceremony on Wednesday 19 October 2022 at the Grand Hyatt Dubai.

To help with planning this momentous day, please read this ‘Information Sheet’  to familiarise yourself with the procedures on the day, the requirement for academic attire, photography and other relevant details.

 

ENTRY TO THE EVENT 

Below you will find your digital ticket(s) to the event for yourself and your named registered guests.

Please note:

Entrance  to  the  event  is  by  ticket  only  and children, over the age of 3 years, require a ticket to enter the event.
Each ticket can be used once only Additional guest tickets will not be sold at the venue on the day of the ceremony. 
Additional tickets once purchased are non-refundable.
You and your guests, will be asked to present the tickets at the venue – please present each ticket (barcode) via your mobile device* or in hard-copy form.  You are welcome to forward this email to your guests so they can enter the venue at a different time from you.

*  Please ensure that your mobile device or email client is NOT operating in Dark Mode as the scanner will not be able to read the barcode.  Please find instructions for turning off dark mode for Apple iOS and Android.

We look forward to seeing you at the cerermony.

